        "Difference between Hardware & Software:\n",
        "\n",
        "Hardware can be simply known as the physical parts you can touch\n",
        "ex: 1- Keyboard\n",
        "2- Screen\n",
        "3- Mouse\n",
        "4- Cpu\n",
        "5- Ram\n",
        "\n",
        "Software is known as the program that runs on hardware\n",
        "ex: 1- Whatsapp\n",
        "2- Web Browser\n",
        "3- Operating System\n",
        "4- Music Player\n",
        "5- Calculator"
      ],
